						               													<description>&amp;quot; The memory game that gets you moving&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Tune up both your reflexes and memory by waving your hand in loops that can sense your motions. Seven game modes available for 1-4 players, including a mode that allows you to create your own music.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;- Repeat the Beat&amp;#10;- Rhythm and Flow&amp;#10;- Versus Mode&amp;#10;- Reflex master&amp;#10;- Musicology&amp;#10;- Freestyle DJ&amp;#10;- Music studio&amp;#10;&amp;#10;(Battery included!)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players compete against each other or the game by repeating sounds or combinations of sounds played by the game. Moving your hand over  a sensor in the loops triggers a correct or incorrect response from the game. Sometimes you must use both hands to trigger a correct response. The game demands both memory ability to replay the right sequence of sounds as well as dexterity in moving your hands to the correct location(s). The non-game modes teach music scales and you can create songs with the correct hand placement in the open loops or &amp;quot;LOOPZ&amp;quot;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
